&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;--multi-tenant-app-name (Only for Azure) The app name to use when connecting to Azure Storage
